title: 25(2) of the Personal Injuries Resolution Board Act 2022 (No. 42 of 2022) and
heading: 2. The 13th day of February 2023 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 13th day of February 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 
following provisions of the Personal Injuries Resolution Board Act 2022 (No. 
42 of 2022) come into operation: 

(a) 

section 1; 

(b) 

subparagraphs (iii) and (iv) of section 7(a); 

(c) 

paragraph (c) of section 11; 

(d) paragraph (b) of section 12; 

(e) 

(f) 

(g) 

paragraphs (b) and (c) of section 13; 

sections 14, 15 and 16; 

section 17 (other than insofar as that section relates to the 
insertion, in subsection (1) of section 54 of the Principal Act, of 
paragraph (aa)); 

(h) 

section 18; 

(i) 

(j) 

sections 20, 21 and 22; 

section 25. 

GIVEN under my hand, 
 3 February 2023 

DARA CALLEARY, 
Minister of State at the Department of Enterprise, Trade and 

Employment 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 7th February, 2023.
